:

*Poznat* je da se u Srbiji uživa u dobrom provodu. (It is known that in Serbia people enjoy good times.)

*Poznata* su imena mnogih bivših jugoslovenskih lidera. (The names of many former Yugoslav leaders are known.)

*Poznati* su nam dan i sat kada će se događaj desiti. (We know the day and the hour when the event will happen.)

Niko nije *poznat* po onome što je učinio u prošlosti. (Nobody is known for what they have done in the past.)

Mnogi ljudi su *poznati* po svojoj nesebičnosti. (Many people are known for their selflessness.)